# APISpectrumBoard - Multi-API Health & Latency Monitor

APISpectrumBoard helps you observe system-wide API behavior using real-time snapshots and status overviews.

## Features
- Logs status codes + latency  
- Real-time CLI board  
- Export to CSV or JSON  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/30_APISpectrumBoard.git
cd 30_APISpectrumBoard
python monitor.py
